@startuml
title Figure 19. Assistive AI CV Builder Sequence Diagram
actor "Next.js Client" as Client
participant "NestJS API Gateway" as API
participant "Google Gemini API" as Gemini
database "PostgreSQL (Prisma)" as DB

Client -> API : POST /resumes/generate-ai\n(jobId, templateId, profile data)
API -> API : build structured prompt
API -> Gemini : send prompt + API key
Gemini --> API : optimized CV JSON / text
API -> DB : persist cv_profile / generated data
DB --> API : save success
API --> Client : HTTP 200 OK + optimized data
Client -> Client : render live preview
Client -> Client : html2canvas snapshot
Client -> Client : jsPDF export
Client --> Client : download PDF

@enduml
